features: 🚨 [CAUTION!] This screen protector (non-glass) and camera lens protector are exclusively designed for OnePlus 12. Before installing the screen protector, please watch the installation video located in the product photos. If small scratches and bubbles persist after installation, don't worry; patiently wait, and they will automatically disappear within 24 hours.

🔄 [Flexible Material & Bubble-Free] Important: The screen protector is not tempered glass; it's crafted from premium thermoplastic polyurethane (TPU), a flexible material covering the curved edges of OnePlus 12, ensuring maximum scratch protection. With nano-elasticity to prevent screen breakage due to drops. Thanks to a high-permeability glue with strong adhesion, small scratches and air bubbles will self-repair within 24 hours.

🌈 [High-Definition & Touch Sensitivity] The ultra-thin design (0.16mm) of the high transparency screen protector delivers bright and vibrant image quality, maintaining the original visual experience. High-response haptic touch technology supports all unlocking methods, including fingerprint unlocking. The visual effect and touch sensitivity during use are akin to the bare screen.

📸 [Camera Lens Protection] Utilizing nano electrostatic automatic adsorption technology, the camera lens protector is easy to install and resistant to falling off. With up to 9H hardness tempered glass, it provides robust protection against scratches. The anti-fingerprint coating ensures cleanliness, and the 99.99% light transmittance is suitable for night shooting. These features guarantee your phone photos remain original at all times.

🎁 [Everything You Need and Exceptional Support] Upon purchase, you'll receive not one but two OnePlus 12 screen protectors, two camera lens protectors, and two cleaning kits. If you have any questions or feedback, our exceptional after-sales team is at your service, promising a response within 12 hours.
